{"tid":1868851,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"梁啓智：香港人平均仲有 17 日口罩","createTime":"2020-02-07T21:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T07:29:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":240,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"f34c130e40b44b10743167b33b07c5e101b2bd7b","tid":1868851,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:15:14.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所最新一期的民意調查問了一條大家最近都會互相問的問題：「你仲淨幾多口罩？」答案是：平均 17 日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBbJ5mg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBbJ5mg.png&h=25920084&s={SIZE}\" />一<br />\n<br />\n不過這兒要做個註腳：正如你去問香港人的身家，平均數未必是最重要的那個數字，同時也要看分佈。有 5% 的受訪者已經冇哂口罩，另外 4% 只可以捱到一、兩日；如果他們這幾日沒有找到口罩的話，其實現在應該也跌到零的了。合共過半數受訪者儲備只有兩星期或以下，十分緊張。與此同時，有 14% 的受訪者稱他們有一個月以上的儲備。按年齡分的話，長者的平均儲備比較低。<br />\n<br />\n呻兩句，這種研究，不是應該政府自己做的嗎？哪些市民冇口罩，政府在有限資源之下應針對性的幫助，這是基本責任吧。對，這個我們也有問：84% 受訪者認為政府有責任確保口罩供應。<br />\n<br />\n另外，這次研究也跟進了香港人對政府抗疫的滿意度（嚴重不滿），對封關的支持度（非常支持），和對醫護罷工的支持度（大幅支持）， 全數和上星期改變不大。醫護罷工多日，民意冇逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n最後加一句：是項研究是香港民意研究所用自己儲備做的，沒有專項捐款支持，不過我都多口講句請大家幫手課金撐著啦。<br />\n<br />\n研究結果<br />\n課金支持<br />\n<br />\n作者 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E4%BB%B2%E6%9C%89-17-%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E6%259C%2589-17-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%2F&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=dd26ec4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E6%259C%2589-17-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%2F&h=14cf4346\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E4%BB%B2%E6%9C%89-17-%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"84710b7d9f5f6a4ac295252e2043f7b98fdc62f7","tid":1868851,"uid":77196,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:17:10.000Z","msg":"按年齡分的話，長者的平均儲備比較低<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e59c2c0f11fdb7bd054eb50ecbca8ebec446cb1","tid":1868851,"uid":68860,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:24:33.000Z","msg":"港共政權連個咁基本嘅調查都唔識/唔會做<br />\n香港人死活? I don&rsquo;t care"},{"pid":"f1457bb27657156efbcd49d9d595f250e532e5af","tid":1868851,"uid":127905,"like":15,"dislike":86,"score":-71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:33:47.000Z","msg":"間野好心執左佢啦 學咩人做民調<br />\n左邊果幅咩圖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbd2f20f712cbc95deea408bcb84137e99ac39f","tid":1868851,"uid":171506,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"f1457bb27657156efbcd49d9d595f250e532e5af","tid":1868851,"uid":127905,"like":15,"dislike":86,"score":-71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:33:47.000Z","msg":"間野好心執左佢啦 學咩人做民調<br />\n左邊果幅咩圖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:58:08.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"c7e589c97db4bf3db3bd6d62c412176e8316c4c4","tid":1868851,"uid":26770,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"quote":{"pid":"84710b7d9f5f6a4ac295252e2043f7b98fdc62f7","tid":1868851,"uid":77196,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:17:10.000Z","msg":"按年齡分的話，長者的平均儲備比較低<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2l